  "description": "Provides placeholders for easily converting text into the smallcaps font.",
  "body": "# SmallCaps\n![](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/AYh4EmYv/images/7d97ee4ba9239348aa4f6723dd661c628486dc01.png)\n\n**PlaceholderAPI expansion to convert text into the smallcaps font.**\n\nExamples:\n\n```\n%smallcaps_this_is_a_smallcaps_placeholder.% -> ᴛʜɪꜱ ɪꜱ ᴀ ꜱᴍᴀʟʟᴄᴀᴘꜱ ᴘʟᴀᴄᴇʜᴏʟᴅᴇʀ.\n%smallcaps_{player\\_name}% -> ᴄᴏʟʙꜱᴛᴇʀ𝟫𝟥𝟩\n%smallcaps_json_display:_\\{\"text\":_\"minecraft\"\\}% -> ᴊꜱᴏɴ ᴅɪꜱᴘʟᴀʏ: {\"ᴛᴇxᴛ\": \"ᴍɪɴᴇᴄʀᴀꜰᴛ\"}\n```\n",
